      • toGuidelineText

        default java.lang.String toGuidelineText()
        Guideline text illustrates a current help for player to understand command as string. A guideline text will be shows as follow: 
         {command_name} {command_parameters}: {command_guideline}

        i.e:
        • tp player x y z: Teleport player to another place
        Returns:
        a unformatted text of guideline.
